data.description: Check out this three bedroom 1 bath home on a great corner lot. Nestled in the heart of Winslow on Cottonwood Ave this home has a spacious front yard with a huge back yard. Updated kitchen and bathroom with a huge primary bedroom closet. Fantastic Location near Schools, Ball Parks, Indoor/Outdoor Swimming Pool. 10 Minutes to Clear Creek Recreation area with water-fishing year Round, Homolivi Stat Indian Ruin Park, 30 Minutes to Meteor Creator or Twin Arrows Casino and 50 Minutes to Flagstaff.
